(240,7,1,'SINGLE','MEDIUM','一棵深度为4的平衡二叉树，其最少结点数约为(Fibonacci相关)','[{"key": "A", "value": "log_h"}, {"key": "B", "value": "1.44h"}, {"key": "C", "value": "h^2"}, {"key": "D", "value": "Fib(h+2)-1"}]','D','AVL最少结点N_h=N_{h-1}+N_{h-2}+1，与Fibonacci数列相关。',2014),
