(291,8,1,'SINGLE','HARD','Dijkstra最短路径算法不能处理以下哪种情况','[{"key": "A", "value": "有向图"}, {"key": "B", "value": "无向图"}, {"key": "C", "value": "含负权边的图"}, {"key": "D", "value": "含环的图"}]','C','Dijkstra要求所有边权非负。含负权边需用Bellman-Ford算法。',2015),
(292,7,1,'SINGLE','HARD','一棵深度为3的平衡二叉树，其最少结点数约为(Fibonacci相关)','[{"key": "A", "value": "log_h"}, {"key": "B", "value": "1.44h"}, {"key": "C", "value": "h^2"}, {"key": "D", "value": "Fib(h+2)-1"}]','D','AVL最少结点N_h=N_{h-1}+N_{h-2}+1，与Fibonacci数列相关。',2015),
(293,6,1,'SINGLE','MEDIUM','循环队列存储在数组A[0..11]中，front指向队头元素，rear指向队尾元素下一位置，队列长度公式为','[{"key": "A", "value": "(rear-front+17)%17"}, {"key": "B", "value": "rear-front"}, {"key": "C", "value": "rear-front+1"}, {"key": "D", "value": "(rear-front-1+17)%17"}]','A','循环队列长度=(rear-front+maxsize)%maxsize。',2015),
