(528,6,1,'SINGLE','MEDIUM','循环队列存储在数组A[0..13]中，front指向队头元素，rear指向队尾元素下一位置，队列长度公式为','[{"key": "A", "value": "(rear-front+17)%17"}, {"key": "B", "value": "rear-front"}, {"key": "C", "value": "rear-front+1"}, {"key": "D", "value": "(rear-front-1+17)%17"}]','A','循环队列长度=(rear-front+maxsize)%maxsize。',2020),
